  ('optician-moex-02728', 'optician', 'optician-moex-106-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於配鏡處方可以有不同的表示形式，+2.00DS/-3.50DC × 045°可轉換成下列何者？（DS：球面透鏡屈光 度，DC：圓柱透鏡屈光度）', '["-1.50DS/+3.50DC × 045°", "-1.50DS/+3.50DC × 135°", "+5.50DS/+3.50DC × 045°", "+5.50DS/+3.50DC × 135°"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:38+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9fffbc71e0c0", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d4a941399c2e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL)
